Definition ZCG_solve (f : ZCGForm) := CG_solve Z 0%Z Zplus Zopp Zle_bool 1%Z (ZCGtranslate f).
Theorem ZCG_solve_correct : forall f : ZCGForm, ZCG_solve f = true -> {rho : ad -> Z | ZCGeval rho f /\ rho N0 = 0%Z}.

elim (CG_solve_correct_anchored Z 0%Z Zplus Zopp Zle_bool Zplus_0_r Zplus_0_l Zplus_assoc_reverse Zplus_opp_r Zle_bool_refl Zle_bool_antisym Zle_bool_trans Zle_bool_total Zle_bool_plus_mono 1%Z Zone_pos Zone_min_pos N0 0%Z _ H).
Theorem ZCG_solve_complete : forall (f : ZCGForm) (rho : ad -> Z), ZCGeval rho f -> rho N0 = 0%Z -> ZCG_solve f = true.
